    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3261750/extras/96357fb1e5f960c0f806bbe0ca839185.poster.avif?t=1744610161\" width=600 height=118 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3261750/extras/96357fb1e5f960c0f806bbe0ca839185.webm?t=1744610161\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3261750/extras/96357fb1e5f960c0f806bbe0ca839185.mp4?t=1744610161\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >压迫》是一款逼真的单人第一人称射击游戏，在 Unity 游戏引擎上采用 HDRP 技术制作。它是由一位热爱恐怖惊悚游戏的独立开发者制作的。体感摄像头和逼真的游戏玩法给玩家带来身临其境的体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这一次，玩家会发现自己身处一个黑暗、阴森、令人不安的走廊，走廊里到处都是异常现象。也许在这些走廊中，他并不孤单。玩家必须克服内心的恐惧，保持警惕，仔细调查周围的环境，解开谜语，发现异常，找到逃生路线，重获自由。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这是一次结局令人惊喜的体验</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3261750/extras/631bd9b9a0778c19bd640483dd119072.poster.avif?t=1744610161\" width=600 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3261750/extras/631bd9b9a0778c19bd640483dd119072.webm?t=1744610161\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3261750/extras/631bd9b9a0778c19bd640483dd119072.mp4?t=1744610161\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >故事背景</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >我们的主人公卢克发现自己在走廊里，地上有一把枪，他不知道自己是怎么来到这里的。他不知道自己是怎么来到这里的，也不知道为什么会来到这里。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >墙壁上的文字告诉他要穿过走廊，找到异常点。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >卢克能否找到他为什么会在这条黑暗阴森的走廊里，更重要的是，他如何才能离开这里？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3261750/extras/c5750fd7d73f3fa2cfee63db56cd72b5.poster.avif?t=1744610161\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3261750/extras/c5750fd7d73f3fa2cfee63db56cd72b5.webm?t=1744610161\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3261750/extras/c5750fd7d73f3fa2cfee63db56cd72b5.mp4?t=1744610161\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >主要特点</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-贴身摄像机视角为玩家带来逼真刺激的体验</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-具有真实 ADS 和无限手势的自由瞄准系统。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-身临其境的音效和逼真的视觉效果营造出惊险刺激的氛围，带来令人毛骨悚然的恐怖体验</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-悬疑故事，结局出人意料</p>",
